		{
			dependencies: ["19F0D6BE6B83B60E"]
			description: [
				"By planting and growing some &5Demon's Dream Seeds&r, you'll get its fruit."
				""
				"While eating it does &6give you Hunger&r, it also has a chance to &6give you its special effect&r, allowing you to &6see and interact with&r &5Otherworld&r &6materials&r such as &5trees and stone&r."
				""
				"Of note, you might want to eat these &6outside the Phase I world generation&r &7(beyond 5000 blocks away from spawn)&r, or else you'll find nothing."
				""
				"Without the effects of the Fruit, these Otherworld materials will simply take the shape of and behave exactly like placed &6Oak Trees and Andesite&r."
			]
			id: "1969E3A133A34850"
			min_width: 250
			rewards: [{
				id: "738C8235F21159E5"
				type: "xp"
				xp: 20
			}]
			subtitle: "Minecraft: Otherworld"
			tasks: [{
				id: "74A075281335BA43"
				item: "occultism:datura"
				type: "item"
			}]
			title: "Lifting the Veil"
			x: 1.0d
			y: 1.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1969E3A133A34850"]
			description: [
				"By throwing down some &6Demon's Dream Fruit&r, and setting it on fire, you can create &5Spiritfire&r."
				""
				"Spiritfire does not deal damage, but can be used to &6transform resources into others&r, making them easier to obtain."
				""
				"For example, you can throw in &6Andesite&r to get &5Otherstone&r, and &6Oak Saplings&r to get &5Otherworld Saplings&r &7(will still appear like Oak Saplings)&r."
				""
				"You may also throw in &6Otherworld Wood&r to get &5Otherworld Ashes&r, and a &6Diamond&r to get a &5Spirit Attuned Gem&r."
			]
			icon: "occultism:spirit_fire"
			id: "0C5ED1A1B0FDB204"
			min_width: 250
			rewards: [{
