		{
			dependencies: ["0C5ED1A1B0FDB204"]
			description: [
				"The &5Divination Rod&r serves as a way to locate &6nearby Otherworld resources&r within the world."
				""
				"To use, you must first attune a block to search for, by sneak-right-clicking a compatible block:"
				"- Andesite for Otherstone"
				"- Oak Logs and Leaves for Otherworld Wood and Leaves"
				"- Netherrack for Iesnium Ore"
